text: Kathleen Le Rossignol (22 July 1908 - 6 March 2001) was a British diver. She competed in the women's 10 metre platform event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1908 births Category:2001 deaths Category:British female divers Category:Olympic divers of Great Britain Category:Divers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:People from Saint Helier
